'''Nobu''' was a group of 4 [[Cargo ferry|Cargo ferries]] belonging to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] in the [[Airam sector/Legends|Airam sector]] during the operations of [[Task Force Vengeance]].

When the decision was made to construct a shipyard in Airam space, ''Nobu'', were part of a Rebel convoy charged with bringing the needed supplies and personnel. ''Nobu'' group contained construction equipment. Unfortunately for the Rebels, the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] had learned of them and readied a [[Battle of Rocrin|trap]] in the [[Rocrin system/Legends|Rocrin system]]. ''Nobu'' were destroyed along with all the others.

